id: pm-25d0
title: "GH-468: clarify or publish the pm SDK npm package coordinates (@unbrained/pm-sdk is 404)"
description: "Dogfood GH-468: package-author instructions say 'latest pm CLI and pm SDK' but npm view @unbrained/pm-sdk returns 404 — authors cannot tell whether the SDK is embedded in @unbrained/pm-cli, published elsewhere, or unpublished. Duplicate check: searched publish SDK npm package — pm-ds3b covers SDK reference docs, no item covers the package-coordinates decision."
