acceptance_criteria: Canonical SDK import/package coordinates documented in pm contracts/help output and package-author docs; either @unbrained/pm-sdk is published/aliased or docs state explicitly the SDK ships inside @unbrained/pm-cli; a 'latest CLI/SDK package coordinates' section exists for agents
