body: "GitHub: https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/issues/468\n\n## Problem\nDuring the 2026-07-06 package dependency sweep, package instructions referenced the pm SDK, but `npm view @unbrained/pm-sdk` returns 404 while the CLI resolves as `@unbrained/pm-cli@2026.7.6`. Agents invent non-existent package coordinates.\n\n## Fix options\n- Document the canonical SDK import path (currently exported from @unbrained/pm-cli) in contracts/help + package-author docs; or\n- publish/alias @unbrained/pm-sdk if that is the intended coordinate; and\n- add a short \"latest CLI/SDK package coordinates\" section for agents.\n\nFeeds the SDK-first epic pm-usfg: the universal-tool story (pm-w89s, pm-cbwg) needs unambiguous SDK coordinates. Related: pm-ds3b (SDK reference documentation)."
